<h2 class="bold font-l">How Could You Not Know?</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Peggy Hill finds out about Nancy Gribbles' affair with John Redcorn... 13 years after the fact. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Late To The Realisation</span>, <span>The Last Horse Crosses The Finish Line</span>, <span>The Slow Thinker</span> </h3>
</div>
<div class="square_ad footer-article-ad main_2" data-isolated="0"></div>
